      "relative_position": 5,
      "properties": {
        "overview": "**You will:**\n\n* Declare and initialize a 1D array of primitive data types\n* Access and modify elements in an array\n* Traverse an array\n\n**Estimated time:** 90 minutes",
        "student_overview": "**You will:**\n\n* Declare and initialize a 1D array of primitive data types\n* Access and modify elements in an array\n* Traverse an array\n\n**Estimated time:** 90 minutes"
